Thanks to [Kasun Gajasinghe&#39;s tip][1], I found the solution in the &quot;suggested&quot; link. Update the following file (replace **7.x** with your NetBeans version):

&lt;!-- language: none --&gt;

    C:\Program Files\NetBeans 7.x\etc\netbeans.conf

